翻译成中文：4.3In exercising the rights detailed in clause 4.1 and 4.2, the Landlord shall: 
(a)Except in the case of emergency give reasonable written notice to the Tenant of its intention to exercise the applicable right;
(b)Where required by the Tenant exercise the relevant rights only if accompanied by the Tenant or a representative of the Tenant; 
(c)Cause as little damage as possible to the Property and make good all damage to the reasonable satisfaction of the Tenant; and 
(d)Cause as little inconvenience as possible to the Tenant as is reasonably practicable.
